countries.name: Europe
countries.title: Explore The Land of Heritage
countries.description: Chase the magic of Europe’s mountains and discover the wonders that lie beyond — vibrant cities, serene lakes, and stories carved in stone and snow.

countries.name: Norway
countries.title: Explore The Land of Fjords
countries.description: Embark on a journey through Norway’s breathtaking fjords — where emerald waters slice through towering cliffs and the Northern Lights dance across midnight skies.

countries.name: Finland
countries.title: Explore The Land of Thousand Lakes
countries.description: Discover Finland’s endless forests and tranquil lakes — a serene escape where reindeer roam free and winter’s whisper paints the world in silver and white.

countries.name: Iceland
countries.title: Explore The Land of Fire and Ice
countries.description: Witness the power of nature in Iceland — where volcanoes breathe beneath glaciers and waterfalls crash into valleys carved by time and legend.

countries.name: Bali
countries.title: Explore The Land of Tranquility
countries.description: Find your balance in Bali — where lush rice terraces, ocean breezes, and temple bells invite the soul to slow down and simply breathe.

countries.name: Thailand
countries.title: Explore The Land of Smiles
countries.description: Step into Thailand’s colorful rhythm — golden temples, floating markets, and beaches that shimmer like a dream under the tropical sun.

countries.name: Vietnam
countries.title: Explore The Land of Timeless Charm
countries.description: Sail through Vietnam’s emerald waters, wander Hanoi’s old quarters, and taste the flavors that tell the story of resilience and grace.

countries.name: Japan
countries.title: Explore The Land of Rising Sun
countries.description: From ancient temples to neon cities, Japan blends old and new in perfect harmony — where every sunrise feels like a promise renewed.

countries.name: New Zealand
countries.title: Explore The Land of Adventure
countries.description: Experience the thrill of New Zealand — glaciers, fjords, and rolling hills that inspired tales of heroes, journeys, and endless horizons.
